column5: Anyone have an idea or estimate on when the ice'll be out on Snake Bay and Whitefish Bay? Thanks!

You can pretty well count on the ice being out by the third week of April. This year might even be a little sooner. You can check the ice-out status of LOTW at this link:http://climate.umn.edu/doc/ice_out/i..._status_06.htm
With the weather we've been getting your looking at approx 2 weeks, 3 weeks tops. ;-)
